              "cost_usd": 0.00041789999999999997,
              "latency_ms": 3758.9274999918416,
              "response": "Snipara helps by providing **90% Context Reduction**, which means it can reduce a 500K token codebase to approximately **5K relevant tokens**. This significant reduction allows you to fit the most relevant content within the 128K context window of your LLM. \n\nIn terms of cost savings, Snipara measures token usage and cost savings through metrics such as **`compression_ratio`**, **`token_reduction_pct`**, and **`cost_savings_pct`**. While specific percentages for cost savings are not provided in the context, the implication is that by using Snipara's context optimization, you can achieve substantial savings by reducing the number of tokens processed by your LLM, as it does not incur LLM costs since it does not run inference itself (the client uses their own LLM). \n\nThis means you can optimize your usage of the LLM and potentially lower your overall operational costs.",
