              "latency_ms": 3158.247541054152,
              "response": "Token budget allocation for shared context collections is structured based on the importance of document categories, which affects how much of the total token budget is allocated to each category. The allocation is as follows:\n\n- **Project-specific documents** receive 40% of the budget.\n- **MANDATORY** documents receive 25% of the budget.\n- **BEST_PRACTICES** documents receive 20% of the budget.\n- **GUIDELINES** documents receive 10% of the budget.\n- **REFERENCE** documents receive 5% of the budget.\n\nThis allocation is defined in the `DEFAULT_ALLOCATION` object, which can be customized if needed (see section 5.1 Budget Allocation Logic). The allocation process prioritizes project documents first, followed by shared documents categorized by their importance.",
